Uses of Package
org.flo.paymentchannel

  • Packages that use org.flo.paymentchannel 
    Package Description
    org.flo.paymentchannel  
    org.floj.protocols.channels
    Micropayment channels allow for rapid tiny payments to be made to a third party once a channel has been set up, using some of the advanced features of the FLO protocol.
